snippet.title: Buttermilk the Guinea Pig, Family Life & Emergency Vet Care | My Story With CareCredit #Podcast
snippet.description:
Amber talks about her adventurous guinea pig Buttermilk and how one Saturday morning, things took a bit of a wild turn resulting in an almost fatal injury for this daredevil guinea pig. See how the CareCredit credit card saved Buttermilk’s life in their episode of “My Story With CareCredit” series: www.carecredit.com/mystory

For more information about how to apply for a CareCredit credit card: https://www.carecredit.com/apply
